race.comment: Open race to close out the card. The well-related WHISPERING ROGUE (7) (half to 2xG2 winner Whispering Brook) has placed two from three around this circuit and strips fitter second-up from the spell. Can improve enough to take this out. MELDUBIOUS (4) resumes here but the form he showed in his first campaign was good enough for a race of this nature. Can play a major role while fresh. COL BURN (12) was well found on debut and didn't let backers down with a solid Sunny Coast win. Don't dismiss lightly. MEET GEORGE (10) maps ideally for this from gate two and should give backers a sight. KILONOVA (9) will be rock-hard fit for this and may earn some minor money.
